==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Debrief
<hw>De*brief"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v.</pos> <def>to interrogate (a
person who has recently experienced an event), to obtain information
about that experience; -- used especially of military pilots or
diplomatic agents who have just returned from a mission.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Debride</ent>⟦br⟧
